Buildroot is a simple, efficient and easy-to-use tool to generate embedded
Linux systems through cross-compilation.

The documentation can be found in docs/manual. You can generate a text
document with 'make manual-text' and read output/docs/manual/manual.text.
Online documentation can be found at http://buildroot.org/docs.html

To build and use the buildroot stuff, do the following:

1) run 'make menuconfig'
2) select the target architecture and the packages you wish to compile
3) run 'make'
4) wait while it compiles
5) find the kernel, bootloader, root filesystem, etc. in output/images

You do not need to be root to build or run buildroot.  Have fun!

Buildroot comes with a basic configuration for a number of boards. Run
'make list-defconfigs' to view the list of provided configurations.

Please feed suggestions, bug reports, insults, and bribes back to the
buildroot mailing list: buildroot@buildroot.org
You can also find us on #buildroot on OFTC IRC.

If you would like to contribute patches, please read
https://buildroot.org/manual.html#submitting-patches

pada PATCH 12
tambahan
Untuk menambahkan dukungan LAN (Ethernet) dengan pengambilan IP otomatis melalui DHCP, kita perlu menambahkan beberapa konfigurasi pada file YAML Anda.

Dalam Buildroot, minimal kita memerlukan paket busybox (yang biasanya sudah menyediakan klien DHCP bernama udhcpc) atau dhcpcd, serta memastikan konfigurasi antarmuka jaringan diaktifkan.

Perubahan pada File YAML
Silakan tambahkan baris-baris berikut di bawah bagian Customize Config:

YAML

          # Mengaktifkan Networking & DHCP
          echo "BR2_PACKAGE_IFUPDOWN=y" >> .config
          echo "BR2_PACKAGE_BUSYBOX_SHOW_OTHERS=y" >> .config
          echo "BR2_PACKAGE_NET-TOOLS=y" >> .config
          
          # Pengaturan agar otomatis mencari IP di eth0 (LAN)
          # Opsional: Jika ingin menggunakan dhcpcd (lebih modern)
          echo "BR2_PACKAGE_DHCPCD=y" >> .config
Penjelasan Paket yang Ditambahkan:
BR2_PACKAGE_IFUPDOWN: Memberikan perintah ifup dan ifdown. Ini sangat penting agar sistem bisa menjalankan skrip /etc/network/interfaces saat booting.

BR2_PACKAGE_NET-TOOLS: Menambahkan perintah standar jaringan seperti ifconfig, route, dan arp.

BR2_PACKAGE_DHCPCD: Ini adalah DHCP Client daemon. Meskipun Busybox punya udhcpc, dhcpcd lebih handal dalam menangani koneksi LAN yang sering putus-nyambung (hotplug).

Langkah Penting Tambahan (Post-Build Script)
Agar LAN langsung aktif saat Raspberry Pi menyala, Anda perlu memastikan file /etc/network/interfaces di dalam sistem target berisi perintah berikut:

Plaintext

auto eth0
iface eth0 inet dhcp
